OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773921770
OL,3,CLeaking roofs and peeling paint:
OL,4,CInside one of Wales' oldest hospitals
OL,6,FBosses at Wales' oldest acute hospital
OL,7,Fsay it is no longer fit for modern
OL,8,Fdemands as calls continue for a new
OL,9,Fhospital in west Wales.
OL,11,FIt was first established in 1949, with
OL,12,Fthe majority of the site built and
OL,13,Fcompleted in the late 1950s. Glangwili
OL,14,FGeneral Hospital in Carmarthen is
OL,15,FWales' oldest acute hospital and on
OL,16,Faverage sees more than 1,000 patients
OL,17,Fa day.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
