OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773921770
OL,3,CLeaking roofs and peeling paint:
OL,4,CInside one of Wales' oldest hospitals
OL,6,FHowever when you walk through the
OL,7,Fcorridors, it is not difficult to
OL,8,Fnotice the building's deteriorating
OL,9,Fcondition. Peeling paint, flaking
OL,10,Fplaster and leaking roofs are just
OL,11,Fsome of the signs showing a site that
OL,12,Fstaff admit is reaching the end of its
OL,13,Flife.
OL,15,FFigures published by NHS Wales Shared
OL,16,FServices Partnership show that for the
OL,17,Fyear 2024 - 2025 it would cost over
OL,18,F#1.04bn to fix the backlog maintenance
OL,19,Fcosts across Wales' NHS estate.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
