PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773921770
OL,3,CLeaking roofs and peeling paint:
OL,4,CInside one of Wales' oldest hospitals
OL,6,FOf this, over two thirds of
OL,7,Fmaintenance issues are considered
OL,8,F'high' or 'significant' risks.
OL,10,FThe estates team works diligently to
OL,11,Fmaintain Glangwili but said carrying
OL,12,Fout repairs while ensuring the
OL,13,Fhospital's services are not disrupted
OL,14,Fcan be challenging.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
