PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773921770
OL,3,CLeaking roofs and peeling paint:
OL,4,CInside one of Wales' oldest hospitals
OL,6,FGlangwili sits within Hywel Dda
OL,7,FUniversity Health Board, which serves
OL,8,Fa population of around 384,000 people.
OL,9,FThe latest figures show that the risk
OL,10,Fadjusted cost to fix the backlog
OL,11,Fmaintenance costs in this health board
OL,12,Falone comes to over #220m.
OL,14,FJust one of the issues faced by
OL,15,FGlangwili hospital is that the
OL,16,Foutpatients building needs a new roof,
OL,17,Fbut Paul Hill, the Estates Manager
OL,18,Fsaid they have no choice but to carry
OL,19,Fout targeted repairs outside of normal
OL,20,Fhours.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
