PN,46805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773921770
OL,3,CLeaking roofs and peeling paint:
OL,4,CInside one of Wales' oldest hospitals
OL,6,F"It's not really convenient or
OL,7,Fpossible to undertake those repairs
OL,8,Fduring the normal working day.," he
OL,9,Fexplained.
OL,11,F"So ultimately we have to target those
OL,12,Fout of hours, evenings and weekends."
OL,14,FPaul and his team also have plenty of
OL,15,Fwork on their hands to maintain the
OL,16,Fplant rooms and often have to travel
OL,17,Fthrough very narrow maintenance shafts
OL,18,Frunning underneath the hospital.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@eO]
