OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773921770
OL,3,CLeaking roofs and peeling paint:
OL,4,CInside one of Wales' oldest hospitals
OL,6,FHe said: "In a modern hospital, this
OL,7,Fwould be engineered out and you
OL,8,Fwouldn't have these types of systems.
OL,9,FThey'd build a hospital with
OL,10,Fmaintenance in mind."
OL,12,FAs well as building a hospital with
OL,13,Fmaintenance in mind, being one of
OL,14,FWales' oldest hospitals, Glangwili was
OL,15,Fconstructed in the post-war era
OL,16,Fwithout anticipating how it would
OL,17,Fwithstand the challenges of modern
OL,18,Fmedical demands.
OL,26,@nD@JOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
