CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773921770
OL,3,CLeaking roofs and peeling paint:
OL,4,CInside one of Wales' oldest hospitals
OL,6,FSimon Day, Hywel Dda University Health
OL,7,FBoard's Head of Maintenance and
OL,8,FEngineering admitted the design of the
OL,9,Fcurrent buildings is not fit for the
OL,10,Fmodern demands on hospitals.
OL,12,F"One of the main issues with corridor
OL,13,Fspacing like this is movement and flow
OL,14,Fto the hospital," he said.
OL,16,F"So if, for example, a patient was
OL,17,Fbeing transported from a ward in this
OL,18,Fdirection, we couldn't pass with
OL,19,Fanother patient or trolley travelling
OL,20,Fin the opposite direction."
OL,26,@tD@AOU|D@[O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
