CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773921770
OL,3,CLeaking roofs and peeling paint:
OL,4,CInside one of Wales' oldest hospitals
OL,6,FPlans for a new replacement hospital
OL,7,Fin West Wales were first proposed in
OL,8,F2018, with discussions between the
OL,9,Fhealth board and Welsh Government
OL,10,Fstill ongoing.
OL,12,FLee Davies, Hywel Dda's Director of
OL,13,FStrategy and Planning, said: "We know
OL,14,Fthat long term the only viable
OL,15,Fsolution is to replace those hospitals
OL,16,Fin some form. We've been working with
OL,17,Fthe Welsh Government for the last 18
OL,18,Fmonths to look at the options to
OL,19,Fdeliver that.
OL,26,@uD@^OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773921770
OL,3,CLeaking roofs and peeling paint:
OL,4,CInside one of Wales' oldest hospitals
OL,6,F"Obviously we do our best to operate
OL,7,Faround the challenges and manage our
OL,8,Fservices as best we can, but
OL,9,Fundoubtedly, we're not able to
OL,10,Fmaintain all the standards that we
OL,11,Fwould want to meet."
OL,13,FIf the plans eventually go ahead, it
OL,14,Fis estimated the costs would be in
OL,15,Fexcess of #1bn, with construction
OL,16,Fexpected to take at least 10 years. So
OL,17,Fit would not be a quick solution but
OL,18,Fit is increasingly thought that a new
OL,19,Fhospital is ultimately the best option
OL,20,Fin the long run.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@TO]
